OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772374275
OL,3,CWoman jailed for attacking hospital
OL,4,Cworker and police officers
OL,6,FA teenage woman has been jailed for a
OL,7,Ftotal of 10 months for assaulting a
OL,8,Fhospital worker and two police
OL,9,Fofficers and racially abusing a
OL,10,Fsecurity guard at the Conquest
OL,11,FHospital, St Leonards.
OL,13,FCourtney Stewart, 19, of Willingdon
OL,14,FRoad, Eastbourne, was sentenced at
OL,15,FLewes Crown Court after pleading
OL,16,Fguilty to three counts of assault by
OL,17,Fbeating and a charge of using racially
OL,18,Faggravated behaviour to cause alarm
OL,19,Fand distress.
