OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772374275
OL,3,CWoman jailed for attacking hospital
OL,4,Cworker and police officers
OL,6,FIt relates to an incident on 21 April
OL,7,F2025.
OL,9,FSussex Police say violence or
OL,10,Faggression towards NHS staff is a
OL,11,Fserious offence, not part of the job.
OL,13,FThey add that all frontline workers
OL,14,Fdeserve to carry out their vital roles
OL,15,Fwithout fear of injury, abuse or
OL,16,Fharassment.
OL,18,FSergeant Kieron Bracey said: "Thank
OL,19,Fyou to the staff involved for their
OL,20,Fcourage in reporting this incident.
OL,26,@zD@^OU
