FL,416,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F415A1772374275
OL,3,CWoman jailed for attacking hospital
OL,4,Cworker and police officers
OL,6,F"I want to reassure all NHS colleagues
OL,7,Fthat we will continue to act robustly
OL,8,Fagainst anyone who assaults or abuses
OL,9,Fthem."
OL,11,FSussex Police supports Operation
OL,12,FCavell, a national partnership between
OL,13,Fpolice forces, the NHS and the Crown
OL,14,FProsecution Service.
OL,16,FIt's designed to increase prosecutions
OL,17,Fand protect healthcare workers, who
OL,18,Fface violence or abuse in the course
OL,19,Fof their duties.
